feat: threaded messaging, cross-space toasts, new message pill, mobile sidebar

Threaded Messaging:
- Cross-space thread reply toasts with space name context
- Click toast to switch space, load history, and scroll to parent message
- Container-aware scroll positioning (messages no longer hidden behind input)
- Backend push notifications notify all thread participants

New Message Pill (Webex-style):
- Floating pill above input when scrolled up and new messages arrive
- Shows sender name with preview text (single) or count badge (multiple)
- Click to scroll to bottom, auto-dismisses on natural scroll
- Clears on space switch and own message send
- slideUpFade CSS animation with primary color styling

Mobile UX:
- Sidebar hidden by default on small screens, shows last active space

README: Added threaded messaging and new message pill to features
